Package: forvoztools
Type: Package
Title: Forensic Voice Tools
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Tu", "JC", email = "jcms2665@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive collection of functions for forensic voice analysis, specifically designed for calculating and visualizing Log-Likelihood Ratios (LLR). Includes tools for density plots, violin plots, Tippett plots, calibration, fusion, intersection analysis, and export of results to Excel.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
